                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d665">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.6363/52a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Italy</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Child</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-05-02T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 2, 1922—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your 11, April 24, 2 P.M. <hi rend="italic">New York Times</hi> despatch from
                    Genoa dated May 1 states that Royal Dutch Shell has concluded arrangements with
                    Soviet delegation for extensive concessions in Russia. Investigate discreetly
                    and report.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
